## ğŸ’¡ Why AgentOps?

- **Open Source** â€” No vendor lock-in, inspect the code
- **Local First** â€” Run everything on-premise if needed
- **MCP Native** â€” Built for the Model Context Protocol standard
- **Easy Integration** â€” One decorator, zero refactoring

